These are Puzzles for 2x6 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-1-1::.
There are 6 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, fanta, juice, mirinda, sprite, tea
The people have 6 different hobbies: cooking, drawing, photography, fishing, magic-tricks, video-games
1. the person drinking mirinda is on the right of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##1
2. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the right of the person drinking mirinda##1
3. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the left of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
4. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left of the person drinking juice##1
5. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the left of the person who's hobby is video-games##1
6. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the left of the person who's hobby is photography##1
7. the person drinking sprite is on the right of the person drinking fanta##1
8. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |    2    |      3      |     4     |     5     |    6    |
| Beverage   | tea | hot-chocolate  | juice    | mirinda  | fanta      | sprite    |
| Hobby      | drawing  | video-games | magic-tricks | cooking | fishing | photography |

