.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-1-2::.
The people perfer 6 different movie-genres: satire, time-travel, epic, comedy, western, spy
6 different pets are kept: pony, chinchilla, horse, turtle, hedgehog, bird
1. the owner of the turtle is on the left of the owner of the hedgehog##1
2. the owner of the bird is on the left of the person watching comedy movies##1
3. the owner of the pony is on the left of the owner of the bird##1
4. the owner of the horse is on the far left##1
5. the person watching epic movies is on the right of the owner of the turtle##1
6. the owner of the chinchilla is on the right of the owner of the horse##1
7. the person watching spy movies is the owner of the bird##1
8. the owner of the bird is on the right of the person watching time-travel movies##1
9. the person watching satire movies is the owner of the horse##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |    3     |   4    |     5      |   6    |
| Movie-Genre   | satire   | western | time-travel | spy | comedy     | epic  |
| Pet           | horse | chinchilla    | pony      | bird  | turtle | hedgehog |

