.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-1-3::.
The people prefer 6 different music-genres: pop, ambient, dubstep, metal, house, folk
There are 6 different nationalities: pakistani, russian, malaysian, italian, indian, mexican
1. the fan of house is on the right of the fan of folk##1
2. the italian is on the right of the fan of pop##1
3. the fan of folk is on the right of the fan of metal##1
4. the fan of dubstep is on the right of the indian##1
5. the fan of house is on the right of the mexican##1
6. the fan of house is on the left of the russian##1
7. the italian is on the far right##1
8. the malaysian is the fan of metal##1
9. the fan of dubstep is the italian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |   2    |     3     |     4     |   5    |     6     |
| Music-Genre   | metal   | folk   | house      | ambient | pop  | dubstep   |
| Nationality   | malaysian | mexican | pakistani | russian   | indian | italian |

