.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-1-4::.
The people prefer 6 different music-genres: funk, hip-hop, salsa, folk, jazz, pop
The people use 6 different means of transport: subway, van, bus, skateboard, train, jet-ski
1. the person driving the subway is on the far left##1
2. the fan of salsa is on the far left##1
3. the person driving the train is on the right of the person driving the jet-ski##1
4. the fan of pop is on the left of the fan of jazz##1
5. the person driving the jet-ski is the fan of folk##1
6. the person driving the van is on the right of the person driving the skateboard##1
7. the fan of jazz is on the far right##1
8. the person driving the bus is on the right of the fan of funk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |   2   |     3      |     4      |   5   |    6    |
| Music-Genre   | salsa  | folk | funk      | hip-hop  | pop | jazz |
| Transport     | subway | jet-ski  | train | bus | skateboard  | van    |

