.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-1-5::.
The people have 6 different hobbies: puzzles, card-games, reading, cooking, board-games, sudoku
The people prefer 6 different music-genres: punk, blues, jazz, soul, pop, gospel
 1. the fan of jazz is the person who's hobby is puzzles##1
 2. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the left of the fan of blues##1
 3. the fan of pop is on the left of the person who's hobby is reading##1
 4. the fan of pop is on the right of the fan of punk##1
 5. the fan of punk is on the left of the person who's hobby is card-games##1
 6. the fan of punk is on the right of the fan of jazz##1
 7. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the right of the person who's hobby is cooking##1
 8. the person who's hobby is puzzles is on the left of the fan of punk##1
 9. the fan of jazz is on the right of the fan of soul##1
10. the person who's hobby is cooking is the fan of gospel##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |   3    |     4     |     5      |    6    |
| Hobby         | cooking | sudoku | puzzles | board-games | card-games | reading  |
| Music-Genre   | gospel  | soul  | jazz  | punk | pop      | blues |

