3. the owner of the ferret is on the left of the person driving the boat##1
4. the owner of the goat is on the left of the person driving the helicopter##1
5. the owner of the goat is the person driving the skateboard##1
6. the owner of the ferret is the person driving the helicopter##1
7. the person driving the boat is on the left of the person driving the scooter##1
8. the owner of the hedgehog is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |     2      |   3   |     4      |   5   |     6      |
| Pet         | hedgehog       | bird     | goat | ferret | frog | mouse |
| Transport   | bus | airplane | skateboard | helicopter     | boat  | scooter       |

