4. the person who's sport is basketball is on the right of the person who's sport is swimming##1
5. the person who's sport is snowboarding is the fan of metal##1
6. the person who's sport is basketball is on the left of the person who's sport is handball##1
7. the fan of indie is on the right of the fan of metal##1
8. the person who's sport is soccer is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |    2     |     3      |     4      |   5   |       6       |
| Music-Genre   | metal | indie  | country     | folk    | r&b  | techno          |
| Sport         | snowboarding  | swimming | basketball | handball | sailing | soccer |

