.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-1-9::.
There are 6 different favourite beverages: milk, lemonade, cola, 7up, mirinda, coffee
The people use 6 different means of transport: car, airplane, motorbike, quad-bike, roller, boat
1. the person drinking 7up is on the left of the person drinking coffee##1
2. the person drinking cola is on the right of the person drinking milk##1
3. the person driving the roller is on the right of the person driving the airplane##1
4. the person driving the boat is the person drinking milk##1
5. the person drinking 7up is on the right of the person driving the car##1
6. the person drinking coffee is on the left of the person drinking milk##1
7. the person drinking milk is on the right of the person drinking coffee##1
8. the person drinking mirinda is on the left of the person drinking lemonade##1
9. the person drinking milk is on the left of the person driving the quad-bike##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |    2     |    3     |   4    |       5       |     6      |
| Beverage    | mirinda | lemonade | 7up | coffee    | milk | cola      |
| Transport   | motorbike   | car     | airplane      | roller | boat           | quad-bike |

