.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-1-10::.
There 6 different types of food: pumpkin, lemon, lime, raspberry, eggplant, corn
The people perfer 6 different movie-genres: musical, comedy, documentary, drama, scientific, time-travel
1. the person watching musical movies is on the right of the person watching comedy movies##1
2. the person eating pumpkin is on the far right##1
3. the person watching comedy movies is the person eating lemon##1
4. the person eating raspberry is on the right of the person watching scientific movies##1
5. the person watching drama movies is on the far right##1
6. the person eating lemon is on the far left##1
7. the person eating corn is the person watching musical movies##1
8. the person eating lime is on the left of the person watching documentary movies##1
9. the person watching documentary movies is on the left of the person watching drama movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |   2    |   3    |    4    |   5    |    6     |
| Food          | lemon | corn   | eggplant  | lime    | raspberry  | pumpkin |
| Movie-Genre   | comedy   | musical | time-travel | scientific | documentary | drama |

