.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-1-11::.
There are 6 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, coffee, sprite, cola, soy-milk, milk
The people have 6 different jobs:  dancer, nurse, journalist, designer, entrepreneur, paramedic
1. the person drinking coffee is on the right of the person drinking sprite##1
2. the dancer is on the right of the person drinking coffee##1
3. the person drinking milk is on the far left##1
4. the journalist is on the right of the person drinking sprite##1
5. the person drinking cola is on the left of the person drinking soy-milk##1
6. the nurse is on the far right##1
7. the person drinking iced-tea is the designer##1
8. the person drinking cola is on the right of the person drinking coffee##1
9. the entrepreneur is on the left of the journalist##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |    2    |   3   |      4      |    5     |     6     |
| Beverage   | milk    | iced-tea     | sprite | coffee | cola | soy-milk   |
| Job        | paramedic | designer | entrepreneur | journalist   | dancer    | nurse |

