3. the person who's sport is snowboarding is the person who's hobby is board-games##1
4. the person who's sport is tennis is the person who's hobby is card-games##1
5. the person who's sport is rowing is on the right of the person who's sport is basketball##1
6. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the left of the person who's sport is baseball##1
7. the person who's sport is baseball is on the left of the person who's hobby is camping##1
8. the person who's sport is tennis is on the left of the person who's hobby is photography##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |      2       |    3     |       4       |       5       |    6     |
| Hobby   | collecting | board-games | card-games  | photography | camping       | drawing   |
| Sport   | cycling | snowboarding     | tennis | baseball        | basketball | rowing |

