3. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the far left##1
4. the owner of the chinchilla is the person who's sport is rugby##1
5. the person who's sport is rugby is on the right of the person who's sport is lacrosse##1
6. the owner of the bird is on the left of the owner of the pony##1
7. the person who's sport is golf is on the left of the owner of the pony##1
8. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the left of the owner of the dog##1
9. the person who's sport is biathlon is on the left of the person who's sport is volleyball##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |     2     |    3     |    4     |    5    |       6       |
| Pet     | lizard  | chinchilla       | bird   | pony      | guinea-pig | dog          |
| Sport   | lacrosse | rugby | golf | biathlon | volleyball | swimming |

